### Chat API Smoke Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@user1Token = mock-1001-USER
@user2Token = mock-1002-USER
@user3Token = mock-1003-USER

### 1. Create conversation (product inquiry)
# @name createConversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{user1Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "peerUserId": 1002,
  "productId": 3001
}

### 2. Create conversation (idempotent - should return same conversation)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{user1Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "peerUserId": 1002,
  "productId": 3001
}

### 3. Create conversation (shop inquiry)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{user1Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "peerUserId": 1002,
  "shopId": 5001
}

### 4. Create conversation (direct)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{user1Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "peerUserId": 1003
}

### 5. Send message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{user1Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "你好,请问这本书还在吗?"
}

### 6. Send reply from peer user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{user2Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "在的,书还在。什么时候方便面交?"
}

### 7. Send image message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{user1Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageType": "image",
  "mediaUrl": "https://example.com/demo-image.jpg",
  "body": "商品细节图"
}

### 8. Get unread count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{user2Token}}

### 9. Mark conversation read
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{user2Token}}

### 10. Get messages in conversation
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations/1/messages?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{user1Token}}

### 11. Get messages with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations/1/messages?page=0&size=1
Authorization: Bearer {{user1Token}}

### 12. Get conversations list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{user1Token}}

### 13. Get conversations list (peer user)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{user2Token}}

### 14. Try to send message as non-participant (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{user3Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "Unauthorized message"
}

### 15. Try to get messages as non-participant (should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{user3Token}}

### 16. Try to send empty message (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{user1Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": ""
}

### 17. Try to send image without mediaUrl (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{user1Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageType": "image",
  "body": "missing media"
}

### 18. Try to create conversation with self (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{user1Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "peerUserId": 1001
}
